    "The \"demo://\" URL scheme is reserved for the built-in demo server. Please enter a valid server URL (http:// or https://)." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"demo://\" URL 方案为内置演示服务器保留。请输入有效的服务器 URL（http:// 或 https://）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The model will be constrained to output valid JSON. No schema is required." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "模型将被约束输出有效的 JSON。无需模式定义。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The selected model will be used automatically for new chats. Choose \"None\" to always be prompted." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "选中的模型将自动用于新对话。选择「无」以每次提示选择。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The URL of your vLLM-Omni server. Default port is 8091. Supports image generation, TTS, and audio generation." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你的 vLLM-Omni 服务器 URL。默认端口为 8091。支持图像生成、TTS 和音频生成。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The URL where your vLLM server is running. Default port is 8000. The app connects via the OpenAI-compatible API at /v1/." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你的 vLLM 服务器运行的 URL。默认端口为 8000。应用通过 /v1/ 的 OpenAI 兼容 API 连接。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These tutorials are designed for the web version of vLLM Playground. Screenshots may look different on mobile, but the core concepts remain the same." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这些教程是为 vLLM Playground 网页版设计的。手机端截图可能有所不同，但核心概念保持一致。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This app connects directly to your vLLM server's OpenAI-compatible API. No middleware needed." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此应用直接连接到你的 vLLM 服务器的 OpenAI 兼容 API。无需中间件。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This server does not expose a /metrics endpoint. Prometheus metrics are only available on self-hosted vLLM instances." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此服务器未暴露 /metrics 端点。Prometheus 指标仅在自托管的 vLLM 实例上可用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This will delete all demo conversations and benchmark results. The demo server itself will remain." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这将删除所有演示对话和基准测试结果。演示服务器本身将保留。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This will permanently delete all %lld conversations. This action cannot be undone." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这将永久删除所有 %lld 个对话。此操作不可撤销。"
          }
        }
